cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes an improved convergence analysis of a specific method for reinforcement learning called stochastic variance-reduced policy gradient (SVRPG). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) since these categories are closely related to machine learning. The paper also involves control theory and optimization, which are related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), respectively.
